## Remote Access (MCP)

If this Claude Code instance connects remotely to {{AGENT_NAME}}, memory tools are available as MCP tools:
- `memory_search` — semantic search
- `memory_read` — read specific files
- `skill_list` / `skill_read` — browse skills
- `memory_candidate` — submit facts to the daily log
- `session_submit` — submit session transcripts for processing
- `session_flag` — flag sessions for priority capture
- `memory_grep` — exact keyword search

